### Test Notification API
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000
@accessToken = YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

### Send Test Notification
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/test-notification
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "userId": "USER_ID_HERE",
  "title": "Test Notification",
  "body": "This is a test notification from JobSphere backend"
}

### Send Test Notification with Custom Message
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/test-notification
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "userId": "USER_ID_HERE",
  "title": "Custom Test Title",
  "body": "Custom test message to verify push notifications are working correctly"
}

### Send Test Notification (Minimal - uses defaults)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/test-notification
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "userId": "USER_ID_HERE"
}
